sellerAgent.name: Real Estate with Connie and Donna

data.description: VERY well maintained ranch home in Tallapoosa WITH a detached apartment. The apartment has its own driveway and entrance. This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home features a mud room and a bonus room off the master bedroom. The lot is a big beautiful corner lot with tons of privacy! The property has new wiring, roof, HVAC and tankless water heater are all less than 5 years old, new insulation and a huge privacy fence in the back yard. There are real hardwood floors throughout the main house. The detached apartment is 1 bedroom 1 bath with a kitchen and laundry. Don't miss out on this immaculate home with an in law suite or a rental opportunity!! Seller is willing to sell furniture in the home as well.
